1
00:00:30,950 --> 00:00:35,940
♪Your secret, dangerous flaws♪

2
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:41,620
♪I can stay close
without seeing through♪

3
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:45,610
♪As long as it's about love♪

4
00:00:45,710 --> 00:00:46,870
♪No matter how absurd♪

5
00:00:47,260 --> 00:00:51,450
♪I choose to get used to it♪

6
00:00:52,810 --> 00:00:56,900
♪Truth or lies, you decide what's true♪

7
00:00:56,970 --> 00:01:00,800
♪I won't overturn it anymore♪

8
00:01:01,040 --> 00:01:03,690
♪I cover my eyes and look♪

9
00:01:03,820 --> 00:01:07,860
♪Is love an abyss or a trap♪

10
00:01:07,960 --> 00:01:14,710
♪I only see the sparkle♪

11
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:37,980
=Turbulent Love=

12
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:42,980
(Seron Port)

13
00:01:43,180 --> 00:01:46,980
(Seron Port Chinatown)

14
00:01:47,060 --> 00:01:50,940
=Episode 1=
=Undercurrent=

15
00:02:26,030 --> 00:02:26,870
Zhijie.

16
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:28,120
Zhijie, I was wrong.

17
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:32,080
I won't do it again.

18
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,470
Never again, Zhijie.

19
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:50,560
How dare you touch drugs on my turf?

20
00:02:56,560 --> 00:02:58,360
Not only touching drugs.

21
00:03:01,870 --> 00:03:03,520
You even got my men to traffic them.

22
00:03:04,750 --> 00:03:05,910
How dare you?

23
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,190
I won't do it again, Zhijie.

24
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,150
Zhijie.

25
00:03:25,300 --> 00:03:27,360
Uncle Kun sent Weihao to
Wugang Street to find the mole.

26
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,000
He ordered everyone
back to the old mansion now.

27
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,920
Including Yu.

28
00:03:35,430 --> 00:03:36,270
But the thing is

29
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,590
Yu is also on Wugang Street now.

30
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:34,600
Your career is average.

31
00:04:35,950 --> 00:04:37,160
There are twists and turns.

32
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:40,240
But you can pull through.

33
00:04:41,870 --> 00:04:44,870
As for having a child,
that's a worst-luck slip.

34
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,310
Have a bowl of my dumplings.

35
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,830
And you'll get a turn
of luck in everything.

36
00:04:50,750 --> 00:04:51,590
Wait here.

37
00:04:51,750 --> 00:04:52,800
I'll go make them for you.

38
00:05:20,750 --> 00:05:22,480
Where did you find such a place?

39
00:05:23,510 --> 00:05:24,800
So secretive.

40
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,360
Mr. Guan.

41
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:30,800
No choice.

42
00:05:30,820 --> 00:05:31,950
Cangfeng is watching closely.

43
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,630
They've got someone
planted in the police.

44
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,040
Cangfeng's trying to go legit.

45
00:05:38,070 --> 00:05:39,430
Evidence is getting harder to find.

46
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,390
I found this recently.

47
00:05:44,270 --> 00:05:45,160
Not sure if it helps.

48
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,680
An informant like this.

49
00:05:49,510 --> 00:05:51,000
I can't ask for more.

50
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,830
Before I die,

51
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:55,950
I need to get you a solid contact.

52
00:05:59,190 --> 00:06:00,160
Pfft, pfft, pfft.

53
00:06:01,070 --> 00:06:03,240
Smoke less, and you'll live forever.

54
00:06:05,870 --> 00:06:08,360
Ziheng got transferred back.

55
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:12,880
Is he...

56
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,880
doing okay?

57
00:06:17,310 --> 00:06:18,150
Hard to say.

58
00:06:18,750 --> 00:06:19,600
Same, I guess.

59
00:06:20,270 --> 00:06:21,190
But not really.

60
00:06:21,750 --> 00:06:22,800
Maybe the promotion

61
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,200
made him more steady.

62
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,230
You guys...

63
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:35,560
Police colleagues said

64
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:37,790
Liang Zhaokun had Cangfeng's men

65
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:38,720
follow us here.

66
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,430
Ji Zhijie has also called me many times.

67
00:06:42,470 --> 00:06:43,310
You go first.

68
00:06:43,430 --> 00:06:44,270
Okay.

69
00:06:55,510 --> 00:06:56,390
Go to the rooftop.

70
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,430
Something came up.
I'll come back next time.

71
00:07:19,180 --> 00:07:20,050
You three go down.

72
00:07:20,070 --> 00:07:20,910
Rest of you, chase them.

73
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,510
Check over there. Go.

74
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,440
PC9527, copy.

75
00:09:33,850 --> 00:09:34,840
Location is Wugang Street.

76
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:12,680
Hello?

77
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,960
Okay, I got it.

78
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:21,960
- I...
- Shut up!

79
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,390
What are you doing, Ji Zhijie?

80
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,120
Are you out of your mind?

81
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,670
From yesterday till now,

82
00:11:25,170 --> 00:11:26,480
you've been with me the whole time.

83
00:11:27,150 --> 00:11:28,510
If you don't want to die,

84
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,550
don't get a single word wrong.

85
00:12:18,510 --> 00:12:19,550
From yesterday till now,

86
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:21,270
you've been with me the whole time.

87
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:23,200
If you don't want to die,

88
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:26,480
don't get a single word wrong.

89
00:12:41,240 --> 00:12:42,240
Where were you yesterday?

90
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,230
What were you doing?

91
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,480
Tell the truth.

92
00:12:45,270 --> 00:12:46,150
If you don't,

93
00:12:46,300 --> 00:12:47,320
I'll throw you to the dogs.

94
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,320
Yu.

95
00:13:01,240 --> 00:13:03,390
Wherever Zhijie went
and whatever he did yesterday.

96
00:13:04,910 --> 00:13:06,320
I was right there doing it too.

97
00:13:10,440 --> 00:13:11,280
Yes.

98
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:16,790
Do you even need to ask?

99
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,840
Look at her neck.

100
00:13:18,360 --> 00:13:20,320
They must have a long night.

101
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:21,480
I saw it.

102
00:13:21,510 --> 00:13:22,550
Zhijie is so stamina.

103
00:13:22,670 --> 00:13:23,720
Yeah. Exactly.

104
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:30,960
It's not Zhijie's stamina.

105
00:13:33,480 --> 00:13:34,630
That vixen

106
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:36,480
knows how to seduce men.

107
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:50,670
But it's fine.

108
00:13:54,030 --> 00:13:55,200
Once you're dead for later,

109
00:13:56,630 --> 00:13:57,510
this incense...

110
00:13:58,480 --> 00:14:00,030
I'll light it out of mercy

111
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:01,840
for you.

112
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:06,790
Don't talk nonsense before
gods and Buddhas.

113
00:14:10,030 --> 00:14:11,960
You know they're watching?

114
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:18,830
You...

115
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,790
Dare you swear to the gods?

116
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,630
You didn't
sleep your way up with Zhijie.

117
00:14:22,810 --> 00:14:24,480
You didn't plot with
your cop godfather.

118
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:25,510
You never stole my files

119
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:26,550
and trashed my place!

120
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:28,320
And today...

121
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,320
you didn't meet

122
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,910
your cop godfather at Wugang Street!

123
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,160
Dare you?

124
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:38,910
I'm not afraid to tell you

125
00:14:40,030 --> 00:14:41,670
that my people

126
00:14:42,750 --> 00:14:44,360
took down your cop godfather today.

127
00:14:46,360 --> 00:14:47,750
Not even Zhijie

128
00:14:49,030 --> 00:14:50,550
or god himself

129
00:14:50,960 --> 00:14:52,120
can save you today!

130
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:12,840
Come at me if you have issues.

131
00:15:13,360 --> 00:15:15,270
I'll handle my guy's mistakes.

132
00:15:15,910 --> 00:15:17,360
No one else gets to act.

133
00:15:20,870 --> 00:15:22,240
- Ji Zhijie!
- Stop!

134
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,320
Yeah, Jiali.

135
00:15:27,790 --> 00:15:29,510
You two grew up together.

136
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,870
Don't you trust Zhijie?

137
00:15:41,870 --> 00:15:42,710
Uncle Kun.

138
00:15:54,600 --> 00:15:55,440
Uncle Kun.

139
00:16:00,150 --> 00:16:02,080
As long as you stick together,

140
00:16:04,270 --> 00:16:06,000
no mole can stay hidden,

141
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,030
and no enemy can't be beaten.

142
00:16:11,630 --> 00:16:12,630
Uncle Kun, you're right.

143
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:14,870
Have some tea.

144
00:16:16,480 --> 00:16:18,840
If Uncle Kun hadn't planted
someone in the police,

145
00:16:19,630 --> 00:16:20,550
we never could have

146
00:16:21,550 --> 00:16:23,000
killed Guan Renjie today.

147
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:26,870
That cop was tough as nails.

148
00:16:27,630 --> 00:16:28,870
No matter how I beat him,

149
00:16:30,200 --> 00:16:31,440
he wouldn't talk.

150
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:32,920
That jerk

151
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:36,200
got scared and jumped off the building.

152
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:40,350
But

153
00:16:41,630 --> 00:16:43,750
I grabbed his phone.

154
00:16:49,150 --> 00:16:50,150
The phone?

155
00:16:58,130 --> 00:16:59,120
Uncle Kun already had people

156
00:16:59,120 --> 00:17:00,600
check the call logs.

157
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,240
Once we make the call,

158
00:17:02,390 --> 00:17:03,550
we'll know who the mole is.

159
00:17:04,310 --> 00:17:06,830
Now it's too late to
turn it off or throw it away.

160
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:09,790
Confess now while you still can.

161
00:17:10,830 --> 00:17:12,400
Or when you're found out later,

162
00:17:13,110 --> 00:17:14,350
don't blame Uncle Kun then.

163
00:17:26,790 --> 00:17:27,630
Uncle Kun.

164
00:17:29,400 --> 00:17:30,510
We're still waiting to see

165
00:17:32,160 --> 00:17:33,880
that vixen show her true colors.

166
00:17:49,480 --> 00:17:50,320
Who?

167
00:17:50,480 --> 00:17:51,320
No one's confessing?

168
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:51,910
Wait.

169
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,040
I...

170
00:18:54,350 --> 00:18:55,190
W... wait.

171
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,240
Wait.

172
00:18:58,550 --> 00:18:59,390
Wait.

173
00:19:01,590 --> 00:19:02,430
Uncle Kun.

174
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,070
I was wrong. I won't do it again.

175
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:05,550
I won't do it again! Please, Uncle Kun!

176
00:19:13,680 --> 00:19:15,110
Uncle Kun, there must be a mistake.

177
00:19:15,200 --> 00:19:16,110
How is this possible?

178
00:19:25,310 --> 00:19:26,150
U... Uncle Kun.

179
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:27,480
That was before.

180
00:19:28,160 --> 00:19:29,400
I swear, just that once.

181
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:30,520
Just that once.

182
00:19:31,070 --> 00:19:32,480
Now that the gang went legit,

183
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:33,880
there's no profit to grab.

184
00:19:34,030 --> 00:19:34,960
My mom got sick.

185
00:19:35,720 --> 00:19:36,590
Needs surgery money, fast.

186
00:19:36,750 --> 00:19:38,070
So I said yes to that Guan guy.

187
00:19:39,270 --> 00:19:40,110
Jiali.

188
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:42,550
I've been with you for years.

189
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,880
I was just momentarily foolish.

190
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:46,440
All the info I gave that cop

191
00:19:46,510 --> 00:19:47,350
was fake!

192
00:19:47,480 --> 00:19:48,750
Fake, Jiali.

193
00:19:50,680 --> 00:19:51,520
Uncle Kun.

194
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:56,510
You mean

195
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:59,590
Cangfeng is broke,

196
00:19:59,790 --> 00:20:02,070
so we beg cops for a living?

197
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,440
J... Just once.

198
00:20:04,880 --> 00:20:05,720
Uncle Kun,

199
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:06,910
please spare me.

200
00:20:08,060 --> 00:20:08,910
By the way.

201
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:10,350
I didn't go to Wugang Street today.

202
00:20:10,880 --> 00:20:11,880
Today, I've been...

203
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,240
Whoever betrays Uncle Kun

204
00:20:32,510 --> 00:20:33,550
and Cangfeng

205
00:20:35,270 --> 00:20:37,070
will end up worse than this.

206
00:20:51,440 --> 00:20:52,280
I'm tired.

207
00:20:53,790 --> 00:20:55,880
If there's nothing else, then leave.

208
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,270
So you do get scared.

209
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:34,030
I thought you never would.

210
00:21:51,920 --> 00:21:52,880
Feishu is dead.

211
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:55,160
You're his boss.

212
00:21:55,440 --> 00:21:56,640
You'll be punished by the rules.

213
00:21:57,720 --> 00:21:58,790
Just thinking about it,

214
00:21:58,830 --> 00:22:00,480
I want to strangle Hao Yu right now.

215
00:22:06,920 --> 00:22:08,880
Feishu followed me since he was a teen.

216
00:22:10,110 --> 00:22:11,400
Besides you,

217
00:22:12,100 --> 00:22:13,310
he's been with me the longest.

218
00:22:28,920 --> 00:22:30,750
We lost Feishu and got into trouble.

219
00:22:31,630 --> 00:22:33,240
But we still haven't
taken down that vixen.

220
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,440
She was the one on Wugang Street today.

221
00:22:36,160 --> 00:22:37,400
If I catch her, I'll never...

222
00:22:37,750 --> 00:22:38,590
Come back.

223
00:22:41,240 --> 00:22:42,680
For now, don't do anything rash.

224
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,920
We must plan before getting revenge.

225
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,040
This revenge...

226
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,200
I will get it.

227
00:22:56,030 --> 00:22:56,960
I promise!

228
00:23:02,720 --> 00:23:04,070
Good job on

229
00:23:05,200 --> 00:23:06,240
this Guan Renjie matter.

230
00:23:06,960 --> 00:23:08,070
That cop

231
00:23:09,110 --> 00:23:10,550
always got in my way.

232
00:23:11,920 --> 00:23:13,350
He deserved to die long ago.

233
00:23:14,720 --> 00:23:16,240
Even though we found out

234
00:23:16,830 --> 00:23:18,960
the mole was one of Jiali's

235
00:23:19,310 --> 00:23:20,270
that Shu guy.

236
00:23:23,030 --> 00:23:24,270
But I still feel

237
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:28,480
Guan Renjie must have planted others

238
00:23:28,480 --> 00:23:29,480
among us.

239
00:23:32,830 --> 00:23:34,000
Check Hao Yu.

240
00:23:35,240 --> 00:23:36,720
Zhijie's darling.

241
00:23:39,070 --> 00:23:41,070
Even though she cut ties with

242
00:23:41,550 --> 00:23:43,830
Guan Renjie back then for Zhijie's sake,

243
00:23:45,790 --> 00:23:47,750
that doesn't clear her of suspicion.

244
00:23:53,880 --> 00:23:56,400
Once the replacement
for Guan Renjie at the station

245
00:23:56,400 --> 00:23:57,400
is confirmed,

246
00:23:58,750 --> 00:24:00,440
let me know immediately.

247
00:25:59,830 --> 00:26:00,790
Looking for this?

248
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,320
Hello?

249
00:26:04,550 --> 00:26:05,390
Zhijie.

250
00:26:05,510 --> 00:26:06,880
Weihao took Guan Renjie's phone and

251
00:26:06,930 --> 00:26:07,960
headed to the old mansion.

252
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:10,760
Okay. Got it.

253
00:26:19,790 --> 00:26:20,830
What are you doing?

254
00:26:33,200 --> 00:26:34,510
You took the wrong phone.

255
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:36,950
I took it on purpose.

256
00:26:39,270 --> 00:26:40,110
Give it back now.

257
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:42,160
Don't you know why I took your phone?

258
00:26:43,590 --> 00:26:45,240
Are you crazy? Give it back.

259
00:26:45,350 --> 00:26:46,400
Why are you so nervous?

260
00:26:47,110 --> 00:26:48,720
Want to see who you've been calling?

261
00:26:52,310 --> 00:26:53,150
Fine.

262
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:54,480
Keep playing dumb.

263
00:26:55,590 --> 00:26:57,350
Then I'll walk you through it.

264
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:01,070
Guan Renjie met the mole
on Wugang Street.

265
00:27:01,240 --> 00:27:02,790
And you were there today too.

266
00:27:04,160 --> 00:27:05,000
Right?

267
00:27:09,070 --> 00:27:09,920
What do you mean?

268
00:27:12,200 --> 00:27:13,240
Are you out of your mind?

269
00:27:14,550 --> 00:27:16,070
The mole is Feishu.

270
00:27:17,030 --> 00:27:18,440
You guys caught and killed him.

271
00:27:18,460 --> 00:27:19,310
What's that to me?

272
00:27:19,310 --> 00:27:21,640
Feishu never went to Wugang Street.

273
00:27:21,750 --> 00:27:23,880
He skipped out to gamble
and lied about it!

274
00:27:27,400 --> 00:27:28,550
Hao Yu, answer me.

275
00:27:29,200 --> 00:27:31,070
Why were you on Wugang Street today?

276
00:27:31,440 --> 00:27:33,400
And why did you ask Guan Renjie to meet?

277
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:35,030
If I hadn't picked you up today

278
00:27:35,310 --> 00:27:37,310
and shot Feishu to shut him up,

279
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,550
you'd be dead along with him!

280
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:50,560
Speak.

281
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:53,480
Speak!

282
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,480
Then let me die!

283
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:08,680
Why did you save me?

284
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:11,750
Why did you switch my phone?

285
00:28:13,000 --> 00:28:13,840
Why

286
00:28:14,350 --> 00:28:16,400
hide the truth from Uncle Kun?

287
00:28:18,200 --> 00:28:19,550
Why did you kill Feishu?

288
00:28:20,270 --> 00:28:21,830
Let him finish talking.

289
00:28:25,210 --> 00:28:26,150
You want to check?

290
00:28:27,590 --> 00:28:28,430
Fine.

291
00:28:29,310 --> 00:28:30,150
Go check.

292
00:28:34,270 --> 00:28:35,110
Then go do it.

293
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:40,480
I went to a fortune teller
for a baby today.

294
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,750
The last person I met

295
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:44,720
was Medium Zhu.

296
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:47,310
If you don't believe me,

297
00:28:47,310 --> 00:28:48,310
then go check for yourself.

298
00:28:50,720 --> 00:28:51,560
Ji Zhijie.

299
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,000
Back then, to be with you,

300
00:28:58,720 --> 00:29:00,640
I cut ties with my godfather.

301
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:06,200
I have no family left.

302
00:29:08,590 --> 00:29:10,510
I just wanted to be with you.

303
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,560
Last month,

304
00:29:13,440 --> 00:29:14,720
I went to the obstetrics department

305
00:29:15,790 --> 00:29:16,630
for a pre-pregnancy.

306
00:29:18,750 --> 00:29:19,640
No results.

307
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:23,640
They told me

308
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,550
Wugang Street is best for
praying for a child.

309
00:29:25,550 --> 00:29:26,440
So I went.

310
00:29:27,750 --> 00:29:29,000
I had no idea

311
00:29:29,000 --> 00:29:30,830
I'd run into my godfather.

312
00:29:31,920 --> 00:29:33,920
He died right in front of me.

313
00:29:35,880 --> 00:29:38,270
I didn't even ask
why you guys killed him?

314
00:29:38,400 --> 00:29:40,680
Yet you're accusing me now!

315
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,750
Hao Yu, not a word you said is true.

316
00:29:51,550 --> 00:29:53,350
Not a word you said is true!

317
00:30:02,790 --> 00:30:03,830
You want to know, right?

318
00:30:04,880 --> 00:30:05,720
Fine.

319
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:07,400
Then I'll tell you.

320
00:30:11,030 --> 00:30:12,510
But Ji Zhijie, listen.

321
00:30:15,440 --> 00:30:17,160
By the time I prove my innocence,

322
00:30:18,350 --> 00:30:20,680
the trust between us will be long gone.

323
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:23,320
I, Hao Yu,

324
00:30:25,160 --> 00:30:27,750
won't stay with someone who doubts me.

325
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:30,110
Between us,

326
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,520
it's over.

327
00:31:01,090 --> 00:31:05,860
♪Don't take amber from my eyes♪

328
00:31:07,740 --> 00:31:11,860
♪I'm scared you'll be swallowed by dark♪

329
00:31:13,300 --> 00:31:15,620
♪Watching you get tied down♪

330
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,720
♪Trapped in the corner♪

331
00:31:17,760 --> 00:31:20,230
♪My heart feels torn apart♪

332
00:31:20,540 --> 00:31:25,860
♪Even if it's an abyss, I'll fall♪

333
00:31:27,730 --> 00:31:31,110
♪Gray fireworks♪

334
00:31:31,350 --> 00:31:34,440
♪Pushing back the bright corners♪

335
00:31:34,860 --> 00:31:37,990
♪Waiting for you to wakeup♪

336
00:31:37,990 --> 00:31:41,730
♪Hurts me too much♪

337
00:31:41,920 --> 00:31:45,210
♪I'm not afraid of the pain♪

338
00:31:45,210 --> 00:31:48,960
♪Even if I turn to dust for you♪

339
00:31:49,390 --> 00:31:51,720
♪Let the neon lights shatter and fall♪

340
00:31:51,890 --> 00:31:56,180
♪Filling every desolate corner♪

341
00:31:56,380 --> 00:31:59,550
♪Don't leave me to survive alone♪

342
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:03,460
♪Still scared, I erase my wrongs♪

343
00:32:03,920 --> 00:32:09,780
♪I pray and confess through pain♪

344
00:32:12,330 --> 00:32:15,250
♪I learned to let go of myself♪

345
00:32:16,000 --> 00:32:18,770
♪I burn away every bitter result♪

346
00:32:18,770 --> 00:32:20,360
♪Just to light♪

347
00:32:20,530 --> 00:32:24,530
♪Eternal fireworks for you♪

348
